MATCH_TOOL: Write
MATCH_PATTERN: \.superpowers/brainstorm/.*/content/.*\.html
ADVISORY: |
  The brainstorm companion server only serves HTML files from its content/ directory.
  It does NOT serve images, fonts, or other assets from subdirectories. If your mockup
  needs local images (e.g., persona photos), either:
  1. Start a separate python3 http.server on another port in the content/ directory
  2. Use base64 data URIs (only for small images <100KB)
  3. Use external URLs (Google Fonts, CDN images)
  Do NOT use relative src paths like "personas/foo.png" — they will 404.
